ğŸ” Key Insights
â€¢	T-Shirts contribute the highest revenue among all product categories
â€¢	Medium and Large sizes account for the majority of sales volume
â€¢	Amazon-fulfilled orders outperform merchant fulfillment
â€¢	Metro & Tier-1 cities (Bengaluru, Mumbai, Delhi) dominate revenue share
â€¢	Cancellation rate remains relatively low, indicating strong fulfillment efficiency
________________________________________
âœ… Business Recommendations
â€¢	Increase inventory focus on high-performing categories and sizes
â€¢	Strengthen logistics operations in top-revenue cities
â€¢	Introduce targeted offers to increase Average Order Value
â€¢	Monitor cancellation reasons to further optimize fulfillment
